1.title: Enigmático asesinato
1.plot: Ignacio tells his mom that he's going out that night. Hoping that he takes care of himself, Clara says "come home early" and they both stare at each other's eyes for a while. Ignacio and Pablo are drinking a lot at Santiago bar. Pablo proposes to change to something stronger and Ignacio agrees saying "the only thing I want is to lose myself tonight". The party continues at an apartment with two women who are Pablo's friends.

2.title: Primer sospechoso
2.plot: Clara and Santiago are shocked after having to stop their son's funeral and ask Prosecutor Loreto for an explanation. Loreto tells them that Ignacio died after receiving a sharp blow to the head. The investigation begins and Deputy Antonio Fuenzalida starts by questioning those who were closer to Ignacio; Catalina tells him that she went to La Negra and saw Ignacio kissing Denisse.

imdb.plot outline: Clara is a successful television journalist and her husband Santiago is a criminal attorney. The day Ignacio, their eldest son, is found dead in his car at the bottom of a cliff, Clara's world crumbles and Santiago must gather the strength to guide his family. They were not prepared for the death of their child ... let alone his murder. Clara's deep pain transforms into an obsession, and her purpose becomes finding Ignacio's murderer. Santiago, in turn, takes on the role of attorney in this case. Shocking details about the activities of Ignacio and his friends Pablo and Gabriel spin this case and Ignacio's family off track. Unexpected secrets come to light multiplying the potential suspects in this tragic death. Their home environment is surrounded by them, and nothing is as it seemed.
imdb.title: Vuelve Temprano
plot: A young man is killed in a tragic night and all his close friends, and family become suspects.::Anonymous
